in ./tests directory:
change patterns like:
h1:Inital Instruction {
  p:this is a very strong:important instruction
  ul {
    li:this is step 1
    li:this is step 2
    li:this is step 3
  }
}

to:
h1:Inital Instruction
p:this is a very strong:important instruction
ul {
  li:this is step 1
  li:this is step 2
  li:this is step 3
}

basically h1 tag should not contain any child elements
apply this to h2 to h6 tags as well
